OT	Serves 4
OT	2 1/2 cups plain soymilk
OT	2 1/2 Tbs. white rice flour
OT	1 1/2 Tbs. large flake nutritional yeast
OT	1 1/2 tsp. low-sodium soy sauce
OT	1 Tbs. granulated garlic
OT	1 Tbs. granulated onion
OT	2 Tbs. nonhydrogenated vegan margarine, melted
OT	1 tsp. yellow mustard
OT	1 8-oz. pkg. rotelli (corkscrew) pasta
